{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.800", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Kollege! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.200", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.640", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt hat Herr Glaser das Wort."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.880", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Statt den Versuch zu unternehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.880", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber Polemik und pers\u00f6nlich verletzende Bemerkungen zu punkten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.680", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00f6nnte man vielleicht einmal die Sache selbst in den Mittelpunkt stellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.200", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das w\u00e4re eine L\u00f6sung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.560", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.400", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.880", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn der Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag wegf\u00e4llt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.560", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "brechen die Finanzen der Bundesrepublik Deutschland zusammen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.320", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrter Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.560", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wissen doch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.760", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir Haushalts\u00fcbersch\u00fcsse haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.640", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar zweistellige Milliardenbetr\u00e4ge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.240", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das seit Jahren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.000", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn man von einem Haushalts\u00fcberschuss etwas abzieht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.800", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat man noch lange kein Loch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.000", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern kommt vielleicht auf die ber\u00fchmte schwarze Null oder dergleichen mehr."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.760", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daher ist Ihre Behauptung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.120", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit der Sie hier die Angst verbreiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.080", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die AfD wolle unsolide Finanzpolitik betreiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.040", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an den Haaren herbeigezogen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.160", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie ist falsch."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.560", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Glaser hat das Wort."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.000", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00e4re Ihnen dankbar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.520", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie nicht immer wieder dieselben Zoten wiederholen w\u00fcrden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.360", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich h\u00f6re immer dieselben Zoten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.480", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Offenbar gibt es also nicht viele."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.160", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In meiner Amtszeit in Frankfurt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.720", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diesen Satz will ich Ihnen einmal sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.040", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil er au\u00dfergew\u00f6hnlichen Inhalts ist\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.800", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "habe ich die Schulden dieser Stadt um 1,5\u00a0Milliarden Euro gesenkt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.200", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie das einmal auf den Bundeshaushalt hochrechnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.120", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sehen Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.560", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie hier eine gro\u00dfe Aufgabe vor sich haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.560", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie auf mein Niveau kommen wollen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.200", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.320", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kommen wir also wieder auf das zur\u00fcck, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.040", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um das es geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.640", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an dem Sie aber nicht arbeiten wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.160", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die Ablenkung in solche pers\u00f6nlichen Scharm\u00fctzel nat\u00fcrlich leichter ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.280", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Ausweichen auf andere Steuerarten steht nicht an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.920", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben hier \u00fcber den vorliegenden Antrag zu entscheiden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.000", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.960", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn beispielsweise die FDP als Partei der soliden Finanzen das Gleiche will, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.520", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nur ein paar Monate sp\u00e4ter,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.360", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann m\u00fcssen Sie erkl\u00e4ren\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.120", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die FDP nat\u00fcrlich auch\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.800", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wieso es ein Ausdruck solider Finanzpolitik ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.760", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Operation zum 1.\u00a0Januar 2020 durchzuf\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.080", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber ein finanzpolitisches Desaster, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.200", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir dasselbe 14 oder 15\u00a0Monate vorher machen wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.360", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da wird sich schwer argumentieren lassen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.400", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im \u00dcbrigen betone ich noch einmal: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.760", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Grundgesetz schreibt vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.960", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Erg\u00e4nzungsabgaben einen ganz konkreten periodischen Bedarf haben m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.080", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn sie ihn nicht haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.680", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben sie den Geruch der Verfassungswidrigkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.320", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine Erg\u00e4nzungsabgabe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.560", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die \u00fcber diesen Zeitraum seit 1995 erhoben wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.400", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat deshalb wei\u00df Gott den Anschein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.200", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie verfassungswidrig sei. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.520", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist auch so solide, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.080", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie es im Schrifttum gut nachlesen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.840", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sofern Sie gelegentlich das Schrifttum zurate ziehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.120", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.600", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wort zu einer Antwort hat Michael Leutert."
   ]
  }
 ]
}